"<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Black Like Whom?</ENAMEX>" I saw <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">at least several</NUMEX> assumptions run through his
commentary on my <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">community</ENAMEX> and public sentiment about us. One assumption is
that <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">at least 91 percent</NUMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">African-Americans</ENAMEX> feel the same way about <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Clinton</ENAMEX>
for the same reasons: He is black, he is great because he comes from a single
