<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">justice</ENAMEX> facts--or that <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">African-Americans</ENAMEX> would ignore the dropping numbers of
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">students</ENAMEX> in college and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">graduate</ENAMEX> school programs, the rising level of blacks
